# Overlay Directory
#
# Place any files here that should be copied into the root filesystem
# during the rootfs build step. The directory structure mirrors the
# target filesystem.
#
# Examples:
#   overlay/etc/ssh/sshd_config.d/custom.conf
#   overlay/etc/systemd/system/my-service.service
#   overlay/usr/local/bin/my-script
#   overlay/opt/my-app/config.yaml
